&lt;h2 id=&#34;six-foot-thomson-turbine&#34;&gt;Six foot Thomson Turbine
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/19.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1000&#34;
	height=&#34;750&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/19_hu_8d06656501c06441.jpg 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/19_hu_ef291f8fadae3e13.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34; A 6 foot diameter Thomson Turbine which powered a dynamo which provided electricity for various processes involved in the extraction of the tin ore&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It also drove an air compressor, the remains of which can be seen lying in the tail race below the turbine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/20.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1000&#34;
	height=&#34;750&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/20_hu_69c06a304168f71d.jpg 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/20_hu_2031d355a70ec89a.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Another view of the Thompson Turbine&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This company still appears to be in operation. &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://thomsongovernors.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Thomson Governors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/21.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1000&#34;
	height=&#34;750&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/21_hu_97c53073134dbc84.jpg 480w, http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/21_hu_73df64810dcee413.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Modern poetic graffiti&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“When you pass me, don’t forget those days gone by when my brave heart beat to the sound of a thousand men’s voices echoed in water”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;river-tavy&#34;&gt;River Tavy
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/p/smeardon-down/22.jpg&#34;
